        </h2>
        <div class="section-info">
            <strong>To update the photos for President or Vice Presidents:</strong>
            <ol>
                <li>Navigate to <code>app/pages/members.html.erb</code> in the GitHub repository and open the file for editing.</li>
                <li>Look for sections with headers like <code>&lt;h4&gt;President&lt;/h4&gt;</code> or <code>&lt;h4&gt;VP of Development&lt;/h4&gt;</code>.</li>
                <li>Above each header, you will find a line similar to:
                    <div class="code-sample">
                        <code>&lt;div class="headshot"&gt;&lt;%= image_tag('logo2.png', alt: 'Engineers Without Borders Logo') %&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>To change the image, replace the above line with:
                    <div class="code-sample">
                        <code>&lt;div class="headshot"&gt;&lt;%= image_tag('https://example.com/path/to/logo.png', alt: 'Engineers Without Borders Logo') %&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>
                    </div>
                    using the URL of the new image.
                </li>
            </ol>

            <strong>To add photos for Project Leads:</strong>
            <ol>
                <li>Navigate to <code>app/pages/members.html.erb</code> in the GitHub repository and open the file for editing.</li>
                <li>Look for the section with the header <code>&lt;h2&gt;Project Leads&lt;/h2&gt;</code>.</li>
                <li>Below this header, find lines similar to:
                    <div class="code-sample">
                        <code>&lt;div class="projectlead-headshot"&gt;&lt;%= image_tag('logo2.png', alt: 'Engineers Without Borders Logo') %&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Replace the above line with:
                    <div class="code-sample">
                        <code>&lt;div class="projectlead-headshot"&gt;&lt;%= image_tag('https://example.com/path/to/logo.png', alt: 'Engineers Without Borders Logo') %&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>
                    </div>
                    using the URL of the desired image.
                </li>
            </ol>

            <strong>To update links in the Join EWB section:</strong>
            <ol>
                <li>Navigate to <code>app/pages/members.html.erb</code> in the GitHub repository and open the file for editing.</li>
                <li>Find the section with the header <code>&lt;h2&gt;Join EWB&lt;/h2&gt;</code>.</li>
                <li>Locate the link you want to update, for example:
                    <div class="code-sample">
                        <code>
                            &lt;a href="https://www.ewb-tamu.org/projects" target="_blank" class="link-box"&gt;<br>
                            &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;img src="&lt;%= asset_path('texting_icon.png') %&gt;" alt="Texting Icon" class="icon"&gt;<br>
                            &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;span class="link-item"&gt;GroupMe&lt;/span&gt;<br>
                            &lt;/a&gt;
                        </code>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Replace the URL inside <code>href="..."</code> with the desired link.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
