            Calendar <span class="arrow">▼</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="section-info">
            The calendar page displays the upcoming events for the EWB organization as it shows on the EWB Google Calendar. The calendar page is accessible by clicking <u>Calendar</u> in the navbar.
            The calendar page displays the upcoming events for the next week. Each event is listed with the <b>Event Name</b>, <b>Start Time</b>, <b>End Time</b>, and <b>Description</b>.
            The <b>Start Time</b> and <b>End Time</b> are displayed in the format "YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM AM/PM".
            <br>
            <br>
            As Admins, the ability to edit and delete calendar events will be available. The <u>Edit this Event</u> button will take you to a page where you can edit the event's information.
            Admins will also have the ability to create events on the calendar page. Any events that are created on the website will show up in the EWB Google Calendar. 
            The opposite is true too as any events created on the EWB Google Calendar will show up on the website.
            <br>
            <br>
            There will be a link provided to the President that will allow for members to have access to the Google Calendar. The calendar will not be seen on the website without this link and calendar acceptance.
        </p>
